<Class name="CM_ObjectUpgraderCAMSTrx" id="18346dea-e4f4-4704-bd98-3429af293dee">
    <superclass name="CM_ObjectUpgrader"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>
Purpose:	Allow CM_TITransaction::camsTimeStamp to be updated partly during the release upgrade and
            the remainder in a background process

Steps:

1. As part of 8.2.1 upgrade an instance of this class will be created for each terminal.  The upgrade process will
   call runConversion for the last 30 days and set that date from which transactions have been updated.
   
2. The BGP must be run to complete the upgrade for each terminal - status gets set to complete when this is done 
   for the terminal.  Once the upgrade is complete for a terminal an entry will be written to the activity log 
   indicating this is so.

3. CAMS will look for an instance of this class for its terminal and check it is not running for a date prior
   to which camsTimeStamp has been updated.

4. As part of the 8.2.2 upgrade, a check will be made for any instances of this class that are not marked as complete.
   runConversion will be called for any that are found.  All completed instances will also be deleted.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="objUpgrader"/>
    <Constant name="STYLE_BGP_CONVERSION" id="ecb9031a-3745-4697-9934-145170abce4a">
        <source>'Convert remaining data via BGP'</source>
        <type name="String"/>
    </Constant>
    <Constant name="STYLE_INITIAL_CONVERSION" id="e0c4ccaa-6a72-4622-afc1-3a3f924a0d7f">
        <source>'Initial conversion'</source>
        <type name="String"/>
    </Constant>
    <Constant name="STYLE_NEXT_RELEASE_UPGRADE" id="b7b6cc67-f5b5-4eb9-a948-c4f829bb9ffc">
        <source>'Update remaining objects in the next relaese'</source>
        <type name="String"/>
    </Constant>
    <PrimAttribute name="earliestTrxUpgradedDate" id="f83d7f88-3bcd-4d2a-8ac1-7bf00191ed7f">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Date"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
    </PrimAttribute>
    <ImplicitInverseRef name="myTerminal" id="35573a52-e6b3-4832-ae21-f9695a354347">
        <embedded/>
